Text: 'Exchange this kind of life with someone Who is in a same position of me and
  also knowing the culture of other country open your mind and refresh your life Style
  because you only Care about yourself and what People think or talk about what you
  have to do with your life right now.

  But a travel always can change your thoughts your feelings and the way you live.

  A completely New person is in your way right now show you how can you approach your
  destiny or your abilities to be happy in the way that you are only changing the
  persperctive'
